title: 08 — Wearable Objects
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify wear and remove actions for WearableTrait items

---

# Take the hard hat
> take hard hat
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Wear it — output: "You put on hard hat."
> wear hat
[OK: contains "put on"]

# Inventory should show it as worn
> inventory
[OK: contains "hard hat"]
[OK: contains "worn"]

# Remove it — output: "You take off hard hat."
> take off hat
[OK: contains "take off"]

# Should still be in inventory but not worn
> inventory
[OK: contains "hard hat"]
